name: Lateralmenu no fragments
tagline: Create un  custom navigation drawer menu without fragments
body:
# Lateral menu  with out  fragments

This  tutorial is let   you to create custom lateral menu,  with  icons according material design guide line.
It's based on [a previous git](https://github.com/Dahnark/Navigation-Drawer-Android-Design-Support-Library) but has some comments and commits   that explain  who it  was  build.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
